{"id":459,"ayahs":[{"number":6,"arabic":"خَلَقَكُم مِّن نَّفْسٍۢ وَٰحِدَةٍۢ ثُمَّ جَعَلَ مِنْهَا زَوْجَهَا وَأَنزَلَ لَكُم مِّنَ ٱلْأَنْعَٰمِ ثَمَٰنِيَةَ أَزْوَٰجٍۢ ۚ يَخْلُقُكُمْ فِى بُطُونِ أُمَّهَٰتِكُمْ خَلْقًۭا مِّنۢ بَعْدِ خَلْقٍۢ فِى ظُلُمَٰتٍۢ ثَلَٰثٍۢ ۚ ذَٰلِكُمُ ٱللَّهُ رَبُّكُمْ لَهُ ٱلْمُلْكُ ۖ لَآ إِلَٰهَ إِلَّا هُوَ ۖ فَأَنَّىٰ تُصْرَفُونَ","translation":"He has created you [all] out of one living entity, and out of it fashioned its mate; and he has be­stowed upon you four kinds of cattle of either sex; [and] He creates you in your mothers’ wombs, one act of creation after another, in threefold depths of darkness. Thus is God, your Sustainer: unto Him belongs all dominion: there is no deity save Him: how, then, can you lose sight of the truth?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4064.mp3","surahId":39,"words":[{"id":7122,"position":1,"arabic":"خَلَقَكُم","translation":"তোমাদের তিনি সৃষ্টি করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7123,"position":2,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7124,"position":3,"arabic":"نَّفْسٍۢ","translation":"ব্যক্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7125,"position":4,"arabic":"وَٰحِدَةٍۢ","translation":"একই","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7126,"position":5,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7127,"position":6,"arabic":"جَعَلَ","translation":"সৃষ্টি করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7128,"position":7,"arabic":"مِنْهَا","translation":"তার থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7129,"position":8,"arabic":"زَوْجَهَا","translation":"তার জোড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7130,"position":9,"arabic":"وَأَنزَلَ","translation":"ও দিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7131,"position":10,"arabic":"لَكُم","translation":"তোমাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7132,"position":11,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"মধ্যে হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7133,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْأَنْعَـٰمِ","translation":"গবাদি পশুদের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7134,"position":13,"arabic":"ثَمَـٰنِيَةَ","translation":"আট","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7135,"position":14,"arabic":"أَزْوَٰجٍۢ ۚ","translation":"জোড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7137,"position":15,"arabic":"يَخْلُقُكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদেরকে সৃষ্টি করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7138,"position":16,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7139,"position":17,"arabic":"بُطُونِ","translation":"পেটসমূহের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7140,"position":18,"arabic":"أُمَّهَـٰتِكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের মায়েদের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7141,"position":19,"arabic":"خَلْقًۭا","translation":"সৃষ্টির","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7142,"position":20,"arabic":"مِّنۢ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7143,"position":21,"arabic":"بَعْدِ","translation":"পরে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7144,"position":22,"arabic":"خَلْقٍۢ","translation":"সৃষ্টি","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7145,"position":23,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7146,"position":24,"arabic":"ظُلُمَـٰتٍۢ","translation":"অন্ধকারসমূহের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7147,"position":25,"arabic":"ثَلَـٰثٍۢ ۚ","translation":"তিনটি (আবরণের)","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7149,"position":26,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكُمُ","translation":"তিনিই তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7150,"position":27,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7151,"position":28,"arabic":"رَبُّكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের রব","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7152,"position":29,"arabic":"لَهُ","translation":"তাঁরই","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7153,"position":30,"arabic":"ٱلْمُلْكُ ۖ","translation":"সার্বভৌমত্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7155,"position":31,"arabic":"لَآ","translation":"নেই","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7156,"position":32,"arabic":"إِلَـٰهَ","translation":"কোনো ইলাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7157,"position":33,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"ব্যতীত","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7158,"position":34,"arabic":"هُوَ ۖ","translation":"তিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_037.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7160,"position":35,"arabic":"فَأَنَّىٰ","translation":"সুতরাং কোথায়","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_039.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7161,"position":36,"arabic":"تُصْرَفُونَ","translation":"তোমাদের ফিরানো হচ্ছে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_006_040.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7162,"position":37,"arabic":"٦","translation":"(৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":7,"arabic":"إِن تَكْفُرُوا۟ فَإِنَّ ٱللَّهَ غَنِىٌّ عَنكُمْ ۖ وَلَا يَرْضَىٰ لِعِبَادِهِ ٱلْكُفْرَ ۖ وَإِن تَشْكُرُوا۟ يَرْضَهُ لَكُمْ ۗ وَلَا تَزِرُ وَازِرَةٌۭ وِزْرَ أُخْرَىٰ ۗ ثُمَّ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكُم مَّرْجِعُكُمْ فَيُنَبِّئُكُم بِمَا كُنتُمْ تَعْمَلُونَ ۚ إِنَّهُۥ عَلِيمٌۢ بِذَاتِ ٱلصُّدُورِ","translation":"If you are ingrate behold, God has no need of you; none the less, He does not approve of in­gratitude in His servants: whereas, if you show grati­tude, He approves it in you. And no bearer of burdens shall be made to bear another’s burden. In time, unto your Sustainer you all must return, and then He will make you [truly] understand all that you were doing [in life]: for, verily, He has full knowledge of what is in the hearts [of men].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4065.mp3","surahId":39,"words":[{"id":8445,"position":1,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8446,"position":2,"arabic":"تَكْفُرُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা অকৃতজ্ঞ হও","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8447,"position":3,"arabic":"فَإِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চযই তবুও়","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8448,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8449,"position":5,"arabic":"غَنِىٌّ","translation":"অমুখাপেক্ষী","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8450,"position":6,"arabic":"عَنكُمْ ۖ","translation":"তোমাদের থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8452,"position":7,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"কিন্তু না","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8453,"position":8,"arabic":"يَرْضَىٰ","translation":"পছন্দ করেন তিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8454,"position":9,"arabic":"لِعِبَادِهِ","translation":"তাঁর দাসদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8455,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْكُفْرَ ۖ","translation":"অকৃতজ্ঞতাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8457,"position":11,"arabic":"وَإِن","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8458,"position":12,"arabic":"تَشْكُرُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা কৃতজ্ঞ হও","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8459,"position":13,"arabic":"يَرْضَهُ","translation":"তা  তিনি পছন্দ করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8460,"position":14,"arabic":"لَكُمْ ۗ","translation":"তোমাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8462,"position":15,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8463,"position":16,"arabic":"تَزِرُ","translation":"বহন করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8464,"position":17,"arabic":"وَازِرَةٌۭ","translation":"কোনো বোঝাবহনকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8465,"position":18,"arabic":"وِزْرَ","translation":"বোঝা","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8466,"position":19,"arabic":"أُخْرَىٰ ۗ","translation":"অন্যের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8468,"position":20,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8469,"position":21,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","translation":"দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8470,"position":22,"arabic":"رَبِّكُم","translation":"তোমাদের রবের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8471,"position":23,"arabic":"مَّرْجِعُكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের প্রত্যাবর্তন হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8472,"position":24,"arabic":"فَيُنَبِّئُكُم","translation":"তোমাদেরকে অতঃপর তিনি জানিয়ে দিবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8473,"position":25,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"ঐ বিষয়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8474,"position":26,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8475,"position":27,"arabic":"تَعْمَلُونَ ۚ","translation":"কাজ করতেছিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8477,"position":28,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","translation":"তিনি নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8478,"position":29,"arabic":"عَلِيمٌۢ","translation":"ভালোভাবেই জানেন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8479,"position":30,"arabic":"بِذَاتِ","translation":"অবস্থা সম্পর্কে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8480,"position":31,"arabic":"ٱلصُّدُورِ","translation":"অন্তরসমূহের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_007_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8481,"position":32,"arabic":"٧","translation":"(৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":8,"arabic":"۞ وَإِذَا مَسَّ ٱلْإِنسَٰنَ ضُرٌّۭ دَعَا رَبَّهُۥ مُنِيبًا إِلَيْهِ ثُمَّ إِذَا خَوَّلَهُۥ نِعْمَةًۭ مِّنْهُ نَسِىَ مَا كَانَ يَدْعُوٓا۟ إِلَيْهِ مِن قَبْلُ وَجَعَلَ لِلَّهِ أَندَادًۭا لِّيُضِلَّ عَن سَبِيلِهِۦ ۚ قُلْ تَمَتَّعْ بِكُفْرِكَ قَلِيلًا ۖ إِنَّكَ مِنْ أَصْحَٰبِ ٱلنَّارِ","translation":"NOW [thus it is:] when affliction befalls man, he is likely to cry out to his Sustainer, turning unto Him [for help]; but as soon as He has bestowed upon him a boon by His grace, he forgets Him whom he in­voked before, and claims that there are other powers that could rival God - and thus leads [others] astray from His path. Say [unto him who sins in this way]: “Enjoy thyself for a while in this thy denial of the truth; [yet,] verily, thou art of those who are destined for the fire!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4066.mp3","surahId":39,"words":[{"id":9640,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَإِذَا","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9641,"position":2,"arabic":"مَسَّ","translation":"স্পর্শ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9642,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ","translation":"মানুষকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9643,"position":4,"arabic":"ضُرٌّۭ","translation":"কোনো দুঃখদৈন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9644,"position":5,"arabic":"دَعَا","translation":"সে ডাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9645,"position":6,"arabic":"رَبَّهُۥ","translation":"তার রবকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9646,"position":7,"arabic":"مُنِيبًا","translation":"একাগ্রচিত্তে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9647,"position":8,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِ","translation":"তাঁর দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9648,"position":9,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9649,"position":10,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9650,"position":11,"arabic":"خَوَّلَهُۥ","translation":"তাকে দান করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9651,"position":12,"arabic":"نِعْمَةًۭ","translation":"অনুগ্রহ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9652,"position":13,"arabic":"مِّنْهُ","translation":"তাঁর পক্ষ হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9653,"position":14,"arabic":"نَسِىَ","translation":"সে ভুলে যায়","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9654,"position":15,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যার(জন্য)","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9655,"position":16,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"সে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9656,"position":17,"arabic":"يَدْعُوٓا۟","translation":"ডাকছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9657,"position":18,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِ","translation":"তার দিকে (একনিষ্ঠভাবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9658,"position":19,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9659,"position":20,"arabic":"قَبْلُ","translation":"পূর্বে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9660,"position":21,"arabic":"وَجَعَلَ","translation":"এবং দাঁড় করায়","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9661,"position":22,"arabic":"لِلَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9662,"position":23,"arabic":"أَندَادًۭا","translation":"সমকক্ষ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9663,"position":24,"arabic":"لِّيُضِلَّ","translation":"বিভ্রান্ত করে যেন","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9664,"position":25,"arabic":"عَن","translation":"হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9665,"position":26,"arabic":"سَبِيلِهِۦ ۚ","translation":"তাঁর পথ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9667,"position":27,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"(হে নাবী) বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9668,"position":28,"arabic":"تَمَتَّعْ","translation":"\"উপভোগ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9669,"position":29,"arabic":"بِكُفْرِكَ","translation":"তোমার অকৃতজ্ঞ অবস্থার (স্বাদ)","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9670,"position":30,"arabic":"قَلِيلًا ۖ","translation":"কিছুক্ষণ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9672,"position":31,"arabic":"إِنَّكَ","translation":"তুমি নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9673,"position":32,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"অন্তর্ভুক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9674,"position":33,"arabic":"أَصْحَـٰبِ","translation":"অধিবাসীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9675,"position":34,"arabic":"ٱلنَّارِ","translation":"জাহান্নামের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/039_008_037.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9676,"position":35,"arabic":"٨","translation":"(৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":9,"arabic":"أَمَّنْ هُوَ قَٰنِتٌ ءَانَآءَ ٱلَّيْلِ سَاجِدًۭا وَقَآئِمًۭا يَحْذَرُ ٱلْءَاخِرَةَ وَيَرْجُوا۟ رَحْمَةَ رَبِّهِۦ ۗ قُلْ هَلْ يَسْتَوِى ٱلَّذِينَ يَعْلَمُونَ وَٱلَّذِينَ لَا يَعْلَمُونَ ۗ إِنَّمَا يَتَذَكَّرُ أُو۟لُوا۟ ٱلْأَلْبَٰبِ","translation":"Or [dost thou deem thyself equal to] one who devoutly worships [God] throughout the night, prostrating himself or standing [in prayer], ever- mindful of the life to come, and hoping for his Sustainer’s grace?” Say: “Can they who know and they who do not know be deemed equal?” [But] only they who are endowed with insight keep this in mind!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4067.mp3","surahId":39,"words":[{"id":10797,"position":1,"arabic":"أَمَّنْ","translation":"সে কি সমান","audioUrl":"wbw/039_009_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10798,"position":2,"arabic":"هُوَ","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_009_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10799,"position":3,"arabic":"قَـٰنِتٌ","translation":"আনুগত্য প্রকাশকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/039_009_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10800,"position":4,"arabic":"ءَانَآءَ","translation":"বেলায়","audioUrl":"wbw/039_009_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10801,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلَّيْلِ","translation":"রাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_009_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10802,"position":6,"arabic":"سَاجِدًۭا","translation":"অথবা সিজদারত অবস্হায়","audioUrl":"wbw/039_009_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10803,"position":7,"arabic":"وَقَآئِمًۭا","translation":"দাঁড়ানো অবস্হায়","audioUrl":"wbw/039_009_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10804,"position":8,"arabic":"يَحْذَرُ","translation":"ভয় করে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_009_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10805,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔاخِرَةَ","translation":"পরকালকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_009_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10806,"position":10,"arabic":"وَيَرْجُوا۟","translation":"ও প্রত্যাশা করে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_009_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10807,"position":11,"arabic":"رَحْمَةَ","translation":"অনুগ্রহের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_009_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10808,"position":12,"arabic":"ر