 Mine who have attained to faith! Be conscious of your Sustainer! Ultimate good awaits those who per­severe in doing good in this world. And [remember:] wide is God’s earth, [and,] verily, they who are patient in adversity will be given their reward in full, beyond all reckoning!’”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4068.mp3","surahId":39,"words":[{"id":12056,"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12057,"position":2,"arabic":"يَـٰعِبَادِ","translation":"\"হে আমার দাসগণ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12058,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12059,"position":4,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12060,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱتَّقُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা ভয় করো","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12061,"position":6,"arabic":"رَبَّكُمْ ۚ","translation":"তোমাদের রবকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12063,"position":7,"arabic":"لِلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদের) জন্যে যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12064,"position":8,"arabic":"أَحْسَنُوا۟","translation":"উত্তম কাজ করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12065,"position":9,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12066,"position":10,"arabic":"هَـٰذِهِ","translation":"এই","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12067,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلدُّنْيَا","translation":"পৃথিবীতে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12068,"position":12,"arabic":"حَسَنَةٌۭ ۗ","translation":"কল্যাণ (রয়েছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12070,"position":13,"arabic":"وَأَرْضُ","translation":"এবং পৃথিবী","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12071,"position":14,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12072,"position":15,"arabic":"وَٰسِعَةٌ ۗ","translation":"প্রশস্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12074,"position":16,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا","translation":"মূলতঃ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12075,"position":17,"arabic":"يُوَفَّى","translation":"পূর্ণ দেওয়া হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12076,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلصَّـٰبِرُونَ","translation":"ধৈর্য্যশীলদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12077,"position":19,"arabic":"أَجْرَهُم","translation":"প্রতিফল তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12078,"position":20,"arabic":"بِغَيْرِ","translation":"ব্যতীতই","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12079,"position":21,"arabic":"حِسَابٍۢ","translation":"কোনো হিসাব\"","audioUrl":"wbw/039_010_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":12080,"position":22,"arabic":"١٠","translation":"(১০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]}]}